{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["Linux"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@dynamicMemberLookup"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPI documents have two distinct forms of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"distributing information such that not all relevant"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"bits of information are available in one structural"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"part of an OpenAPI Document."}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Documents can contain references. This is great","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"because authors can make one part of an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenAPI document more concise by referencing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a component instead of writing it inline and it also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allows shared definitions to be re-used throughout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the document.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Documents can define and override certain things at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"different levels of their structure. For example, a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"document may define a shared set of Security","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Requirements at the root and then override those","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Security Requirements for particular Operations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Both of these features of OpenAPI documents make it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"impossible to answer certain questions about a particular","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"route or endpoint without looking to multiple disparate parts","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the document and then applying certain rules to determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the relevant semantic definition of the route or endpoint being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"studied.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPIKit defines canonical forms (i.e. the only true definitions)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of endpoints, routes, and the whole document. These types (named"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedEndpoint"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedRoute"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"each allow you to get complete information about the respective components"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"without looking to other parts of the document."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Example","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You want to know what all of the parameters for a particular "},{"code":"PATCH","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" endpoint are."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Without the "},{"code":"ResolvedEndpoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" type, you would need to look at the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"OpenAPI.Operation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" representing the endpoint, the "},{"code":"OpenAPI.PathItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"representing the route containing the endpoint, and you would need to potentially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resolve references to the "},{"code":"OpenAPI.Components","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With "},{"code":"ResolvedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the same task is much simpler:"}]},{"code":["let document: OpenAPI.Document = ...","","let resolvedDocument = try document","    .locallyDereferenced()","    .resolved()","","let endpoint = resolvedDocument","    .routesByPath[\"\/example\/path\"]!.patch!","","\/\/ This will be all parameters defined anywhere that","\/\/ apply to this endpoint:","let parameters = endpoint.parameters"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openapikit\/resolveddocument"]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/endpoints","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/paths","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routes","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routesByPath","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/security","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/underlyingDocument"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/subscript(dynamicMember:)"],"title":"Subscripts"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/Equatable-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A resolved document is a fully dereferenced"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPI document that has been further distilled"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to canonical representations of each component. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":" by calling the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resolved()"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method on a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DereferencedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"sections":[],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/SQ"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10OpenAPIKit16ResolvedDocumentV","title":"ResolvedDocument","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"modules":[{"name":"OpenAPIKit"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}]},"references":{"doc://OpenAPIKit/documentation/OpenAPIKit/ResolvedDocument/subscript(dynamicMember:)":{"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"subscript","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"T"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dynamicMember"},{"kind":"text","text":" _: "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s7KeyPathC","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"KeyPath"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10OpenAPIKit0A3APIO","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OpenAPI"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10OpenAPIKit0A3APIO8DocumentV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Document"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"T"},{"kind":"text","text":">) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"T"